  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110187926283\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110187926283\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140327_2/isuhani_1395910868609p6G7R_JPEG/P3272704.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"421\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth: 550px; rheight: 421px;\" id=\"20140327_2/isuhani_1395910868609p6G7R_JPEG/P3272704.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A7B6530B')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20140327_2/isuhani_1395910868609p6G7R_JPEG/P3272704.JPG?type=w3\"></div><div align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">12월부터 3~4개월을 이수한의원과 함께 한 환자분께서 그동안 잘 치료해주셔서 감사하다고 &nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">맛있는 오렌지를 선물로 주셨습니다.&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">힘든 치료를 꾸준히 잘 받으신 환자분께 저희가 더 감사한데 말이죠.</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><div align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/brown_and_cony\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://blogimgs.pstatic.net/sticker/pc/brown_and_cony/original/20.png\" style=\"border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\" alt=\"brown_and_cony-20\"></a></div><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">치료가 잘 끝나 활짝 웃으시는 모습도 저희에게 큰~~~선물입니다^^</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
